# Keep the published tarball limited to the files this package actually ships.
# npm only consults .gitignore/.npmignore in the SAME package directory (not the repo-root
# .gitignore), so without this, a locally-generated Python bytecode cache under scripts/
# (created by simply running mouselock-helper.py, e.g. via the hooks/launcher test suites)
# would leak into `npm pack` output even though it's harmless build noise.
__pycache__/
*.pyc
